
Instalação:
Zoio The Green Eye - ztge
Plasma Desktop Only
Automático, BTRFS + SWAP em Arquivo

Ajustar DPI
Ajustar brilho de tela
Ajustar RedShift

# First boot:
sudo systemctl enable sshd
sudo systemctl start sshd

# PACMAN
sudo pacman -S iperf traceroute arp-scan speedtest-cli samba sshpass curl rclone openvpn steam qbittorrent \
docker-buildx docker \
p7zip cronie zip unzip dialog btrfs-progs cifs-utils cmatrix \
torbrowser-launcher rdesktop k3b audacity wine thunderbird libreoffice libreoffice-fresh-pt-br thunderbird-i18n-pt-br vlc kpat gimp blender \
inxi btop iotop \
qemu-full qemu-base libvirt-dbus bridge-utils virt-manager ovmf dnsmasq \
parallel nmap \
wine

USE VULKAN-RADEON and lib32-vulkan-radeon
AMDVLK is the old one.

# YAY
yay -S upscayl freetube-bin gnome-disk-utility rpi-imager anydesk-bin microsoft-edge-stable-bin google-chrome opera

sudo systemctl enable cronie
sudo systemctl start cronie

sudo systemctl enable docker
sudo systemctl start docker

sudo systemctl enable libvirtd
sudo systemctl start libvirtd

sudo usermod -aG libvirt-qemu $USER
sudo usermod -aG libvirt $USER

sudo cp ~/.config/kwinoutputconfig.json /var/lib/sddm/.config/
sudo chown sddm:sddm /var/lib/sddm/.config/kwinoutputconfig.json

sudo nano /etc/sddm.conf.d/virtualkbd.conf
[General]
InputMethod=qtvirtualkeyboard

Configuração do KDE:
Teclado > Teclado Virtual > Habilitar Maliit
Teclado > Atalho > Monitor do Sistema: CTRL+ALT+DEL
Multimidia > Procurar desativar procurar musicbrains e freedb
Tablet de Desenho..... meo
Gerenciamento de Janelas > Comportamento de Janelas > FOCO > 300ms to 150ms
Gerenciamento de Janelas > Areas de Trabalho Virtuais ?

# ROCm
sudo pacman -S rocm-hip-runtime rocm-opencl-runtime rocminfo opencl-headers opencl-clhpp radeontop
Edit /etc/profile:
append_path '/opt/rocm/hip/bin'
append_path '/opt/rocm/bin'
# reboot
